CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 21, 1956, pg. 27, reads: "Rebounding - Macedonia's Carl Lawrence comes down with a rebound that he captured from Allan James of Holy Cross in feature Church League contest on the Centre Avenue YMCA floor last Saturday. Holy Cross won, 41-36.  Looking on at the right are Carl Dorsey of the Crusaders and Strothers of Macedonia. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Church league basketball game between Holy Cross and Macedonia teams, including players Carl Lawrence, Allan James, Carl Dorsey, and Strothers, in Centre Avenue YMCA
